Definitions.Name: DeleteObsoleteAnnotation
Definitions.Message: '{0:scanTarget}' contains a call to the SAL v1 '{1:obsoleteApi}' annotation and should be removed as it is obsolete or redundant in SAL v2.

Definitions.Name: ReplaceObsoleteAnnotation
Definitions.Message: '{0:scanTarget}' contains a call to the SAL v1 '{1:obsoleteApi}' annotation and should be replaced for '{2:newApi}'.
Definitions.Description: SAL 1 can be replaced with SAL 2.

fix.Description: Replace '[returnvalue: SA_Post( Deref=(1), Null=SA_Yes, NullTerminated=SA_No )]' for '_At_(*return, _Ret_null_ _Ret1_impl_(__notzterm_impl))'.

Definitions.Name: ConvertObsoleteAnnotation
Definitions.Message: '{0:scanTarget}' contains a call to the SAL v1 '{1:obsoleteApi}' annotation and should be converted manually.
Definitions.Description: Conversion from SAL 1 to SAL 2 cannot be automatically done.
